strial agricultural finan cial and political conditions through out the United StateB It discovers in the foreground he says that both major political parties have overlooked the greatest issue in the public mind which is the cost of living It also shows he states that the country is on a sound eco nomic basis with the wave of extra vagance subsiding saving increasing wholesalers and retailers optimistic over the winter outlook and a grow ing disposition for hard work altho the individual productivity of labor is not yet showing much evidence of in crease Made Careful Investigation Mr"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-08-25T19:29:03.298Z", "group": ["ndnp/ndhi", "state-histrorical-society-of-north-dakota-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn88076421/1920-10-07/ed-1/?sp=6", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ndhi:batch_ndhi_jud_ver01:data:sn88076421:00212476067:1920100701:0592/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=257&w=181", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ndhi:batch_ndhi_jud_ver01:data:sn88076421:00212476067:1920100701:0592/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=515&w=363", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ndhi:batch_ndhi_jud_ver01:data:sn88076421:00212476067:1920100701:0592/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1030&w=726", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ndhi/batch_ndhi_jud_ver01/data/sn88076421/00212476067/1920100701/0592.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["north dakota", "united states", "ward", "minot"], "location_city": ["minot"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["ward"], "location_state": ["north dakota"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["4", "0", "2", "7", "1", "6", "sn88076421", "0000000006"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn